author: Fextralife
description:
The Duskbloods NEW Gameplay INFO - Character Customization, Maps, Bloodsworn & MORE!
In this The Duskbloods video, we're going to be talking about everything we know about this game. If you haven't seen it recently. Nintendo posted to their blog an Interview they did with Hidetaka Miyazaki, who is the game director for Duskbloods, where they asked him questions about how the game plays, what it's like, and more. So if you want to know more and learn what this game is all about, then watch on for some helpful information
